text: Cincotta () is an Italian surname. Its country of highest prevalence is not Italy but the United States, with significantly smaller populations in Italy, Argentina and Australia.http://forebears.io/surnames/cincotta ==Notable people== * Gale Cincotta (1929-2001), American activist * George A.
